{
  "texts": [
    "It was the best performing distance based classifier in the bake off.",
    "Elastic distances can be slow, and EE requires cross validation to find the weights of each classifier in the ensemble.",
    "A caching mechanism was proposed to help speed up fitting the classifier (Tan et al. 2020) and alternative speed ups were described in Oastler and Lines (2019).",
    "The latter speed up is the version of EE we use in our experiments.",
    "Proximity Forest (PF) (Lucas et al. 2019) is an ensemble of Proximity Tree based classifiers."
  ]
}